This paper is about training deep neural networks for machine learning problems, which is a topic that falls under several sub-categories of computer science. The most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), as the paper specifically discusses the challenges of training neural networks for machine learning tasks. The next likely sub-category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), as the paper focuses on deep neural networks and their optimization. The paper also touches on topics related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and signal processing (cs.SI), which are all relevant to the field of machine learning and neural networks.
